title: Swede looking for fun people to play with
body:
Hey! 19 Year old Swede here just transferred to Oceania from EUW the other day since i'm going to be residing in Australia for a couple of months. Looking for people to play with and have fun with (tryharding works aswell). Getting a new headset in a day or two so preferably premades with voice comms!

Im an adc main ranging between D5-D3 back in EUW

IGN: WastedCamel

hit me up :)
